  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This prospective study evaluates the effect of DHEA supplementation on markers of ovarian
      reserve in women with diminished ovarian reserve.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Ovarian reserve markers, such as FSH, estradiol, AMH, ovarian volume and antral follicle
      counts will be monitored on DHEA supplementation in a prospective fashion.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
